These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
Movie-Genre: superhero, epic
Sport: water-polo, badminton
Transport: trike, boat
1. Transport:boat is on the left or right of Sport:badminton##3
2. Beverage:soy-milk is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:epic == Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
4. Transport:boat is on the right of Transport:trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | superhero   |
| Sport         | badminton | water-polo |
| Transport     | trike | boat    |

