2. Movie-Genre:adventure == Transport:trike##1
3. Food:eggplant is on the right of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | grapefruit     | eggplant |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure  |
| Pet           | cat         | goldfish     |
| Transport     | roller   | trike    |

